content: That's a lot of great advice! I think I'll try to set reminders to drink water throughout the day, especially on Fridays when I have a lot of meetings. I'll also try to mix up my snacks and add more fruits and veggies to my meals. Speaking of fruits, I've been having a sweet tooth lately and ended up buying a bag of cookies from the bakery near my office. Do you have any suggestions on how to curb my sugar cravings and make healthier choices?
